This template is used by the other [[BoardGameGeek]] external link templates:
* {{tl|bgg title}}
* {{tl|BoardGameGeek designer}}
* {{tl|BoardGameGeek publisher}}
* {{tl|BoardGameGeek wiki}}

== Usage ==

=== Single link ===
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>SECTION</var>|<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>SECTION</var>|<var>ID</var>|<var>NAME</var>}}

Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}<var>SECTION</var>|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}<var>SECTION</var>|id{{=}}<var>ID</var>|name{{=}}<var>NAME</var>}}

=== Multiple links using same ''section'' ===
Unnamed parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>SECTION</var>|<var>ID1</var>|<var>NAME1</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|<var>SECTION</var>|<var>ID1</var>|<var>NAME1</var>|<var>ID2</var>|<var>NAME2</var>|<var>ID3</var>|<var>NAME3</var>}}

Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}<var>SECTION</var>|id1{{=}}<var>ID</var>|name1{{=}}<var>NAME</var>|id2{{=}}<var>ID2</var>|name2{{=}}<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}<var>SECTION</var>|id1{{=}}<var>ID1</var>|name1{{=}}<var>NAME1</var>|id2{{=}}<var>ID2</var>|name2{{=}}<var>NAME2</var>id3{{=}}<var>ID3</var>|name3{{=}}<var>NAME3</var>}}

=== Multiple links using different ''section'' ===
Named parameters:
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section1{{=}}<var>SECTION1</var>|id1{{=}}<var>ID1</var>|name1{{=}}<var>NAME1</var>|section2{{=}}<var>SECTION2</var>|id2{{=}}<var>ID2</var>|name2{{=}}<var>NAME2</var>}}
: {{tlc|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section1{{=}}<var>SECTION1</var>|id1{{=}}<var>ID1</var>|name1{{=}}<var>NAME1</var>|section2{{=}}<var>SECTION2</var>|id2{{=}}<var>ID2</var>|name2{{=}}<var>NAME2</var>|section3{{=}}<var>SECTION3</var>|id3{{=}}<var>ID3</var>|name3{{=}}<var>NAME3</var>}}

== Examples ==

=== Single link ===
''Usage with article name as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|2557}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}boardgame|id{{=}}2557}}
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|2557}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section=boardgame|id=2557}}

''Usage with name parameter as link text:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|2557|Castle Risk}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}boardgame|id{{=}}2557|name{{=}}Castle Risk}}
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|2557|Castle Risk}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section=boardgame|id=2557|name=Castle Risk}}

=== Multiple links using same ''section'' ===
''Usage with two links:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|54|Tikal|855|Java}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}boardgame|id1{{=}}54|name1{{=}}Tikal|id2{{=}}855|name2{{=}}Java}}
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|54|Tikal|855|Java}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section=boardgame|id1=54|name1=Tikal|id2=855|name2=Java}}

''Usage with three links:''
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|54|Tikal|855|Java|2955|Mexica}}
: {{tlc|a=1|{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section{{=}}boardgame|id1{{=}}54|name1{{=}}Tikal|id2{{=}}855|name2{{=}}Java|id3{{=}}2955|name3{{=}}Mexica}}
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|boardgame|54|Tikal|855|Java|2955|Mexica}}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}}|section=boardgame|id1=54|name1=Tikal|id2=855|name2=Java|id3=2955|name3=Mexica}}

